		<h1 class="entry-title">getting started with rails 2 &#8211; day 2</h1>		<div class="entry-meta"><span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="https://www.ultrasaurus.com/2008/12/getting-started-with-rails-2-day-2/" title="11:22 am" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2008-12-14T11:22:46-08:00" pubdate>December 14, 2008</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://www.ultrasaurus.com/author/sarah/" title="View all posts by sarah" rel="author">sarah</a></span></span>		<span class="sep"> | </span>
		<span class="comments-link">
			<a href="https://www.ultrasaurus.com/2008/12/getting-started-with-rails-2-day-2/#comments"><strong>1</strong> Reply</a>		</span>
		</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
